Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.36,0:39:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's love! It's love!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.40,0:39:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogawa-kun, you kids taught me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.86,0:39:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.78,0:39:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Without love, real sex cannot take place!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.16,0:39:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.62,0:39:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.67,0:39:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.71,0:39:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel great.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.55,0:39:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.30,0:39:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san! You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.97,0:39:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God! I was worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.14,0:39:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your lower half out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.23,0:39:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,\NJeez! I lower my guard for a second,\Nand this is hat happens.
