Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.53,0:39:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.03,0:39:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was this video, that brought\Nthe two of them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.57,0:40:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching it deeply moved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.83,0:40:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Masako's mother was an associate of mine\Nwhen I used to be an assistant director.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.62,0:40:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally was able to fulfill my promise to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.17,0:40:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.84,0:40:14.01,Default_I,,0,0,0,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.01,0:40:17.22,Default_I,,0,0,0,,that guerrilla video became a big hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.72,0:40:21.64,Default_I,,0,0,0,,Because of it, Gondo and Ogawa got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.27,0:40:26.10,Default_I,,0,0,0,,This is my first time attending a wedding.
